author: brane
msg: "Are we visible from the earth?" I asked.
"I knew someone -- who was interested in astronomy. It
occurred to me that it would be odd if -- my friend -- chanced
to be looking through a telescope and should chance to see us."
"It would need the most powerful telescope on earth even
now to see us as the minutest speck."
